Package: multiomicsretina
Title: Reproducible Multi-Omics Integration Pipeline for Human Retinal Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Project", "Maintainer", email = "maintainer@example.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Research-oriented R pipeline for preprocessing, MOFA2 integration,
    downstream interpretation, and stability assessment of proteomics,
    lipidomics, and metabolomics data from human retinal studies.
